name: TRIP REPORT | Delta Air Lines 717-200 (MAIN CABIN) Atlanta to Huntsville
description:
Hello everyone, and welcome to my latest trip report, on board this Delta 717-200 on a short hop from Atlanta to Huntsville in Economy Class (Main Cabin)! Delta's 717 is always nice to fly on.

I'm still new to making trip reports, so I welcome any feedback or suggestions for future ones! Hope you all enjoy.

Thanks for watching!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

VIDEO LOG:
00:05 - Walking out of Concourse T
01:40 - Boarding the "Plane Train"
03:10 - At the gate
04:35 - On board
05:40 - In Flight
12:30 - Walking through Huntsville's terminal to baggage claim.
